                                        <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne1" aria-expanded="true">What is a residential proxy?<span></span></a>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="collapseOne1" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                            <div class="card-body">A residential proxy is a proxy that represents a regular user. The target will not see that you are using a proxy, and the proxy is also not located in a data center. Thus the IP has a better reputation.</div>
